heading: Whispering Vault Dungeon Guide
content: Whispering Vault is one of a few dungeons in the game featuring teleporters. You will destroy two and then take the teleporter back to the entrance. It's a clever way of avoiding backtracking. You'll find the here for Rogues. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
